name: Data Waves - Monochrome Edition
description: Boiling inside from the fear of missing out, you can feel it, all these data going through your body, through your cells, leaving only the bitter impression that you won't catch up. There's too much information out there, and all you will ever perceive is just a tiny glimpse of what lies around... (20s seamless loop - 1080x1080 - 60fps - created by @ufunk_parse)
